# Web3Forms access key — get one for free at https://web3forms.com
# Sign up with info@dssmp.gr to send submissions to that inbox.
# This value is inlined into the client bundle by Vite at build time.
# Web3Forms keys are designed to be public (scoped server-side to one inbox), so this is safe.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
